dcterms:description: The dataset contains 387 mammography images from 200 patients who are classified as ACR BI-RADS category 4 and 5 with documented calciﬁcations from the original radiological reports. All cases were confirmed breast cancers from biopsy tests. Descriptors of morphology and distribution were annotated by a senior radiological technologist and carefully reviewed by two senior radiologists in a joint meeting.
dcterms:title: Full field digital mammogram dataset
